   <indicator measure="5">
    <title>
     <narrative xml:lang="EN">Results expected</narrative>
     <narrative xml:lang="FR">R&#xE9;sultats escompt&#xE9;s</narrative>
    </title>
    <description>
     <narrative xml:lang="FR">Les r&#xE9;sultats attendus de ce projet comprennent: (1) L&#x2019;augmentation de 35 % du volume des services financiers offerts aux exploitants agricoles de petites et de moyennes tailles ; (2) L&#x2019;augmentation de 30 % de la couverture de l&#x2019;assurance agricole ; (3) Augmentation du microcr&#xE9;dit rural dans 20 municipalit&#xE9;s affect&#xE9;es par le conflit arm&#xE9;, avec 50% des pr&#xEA;ts accord&#xE9;s &#xE0; des femmes; (4) Le renforcement  de la capacit&#xE9; de gestion d&#x2019;une exploitation agricole d&#x2019;au moins 5 000 agriculteurs, dont 3 000 femmes.</narrative>
     <narrative xml:lang="EN">The expected results for this project include: (1) 35% increase in loans to small and medium-scale farmers; (2) 30% increase in agricultural insurance coverage to small and medium-scale farmers; (3) Increased availability of micro-credit in 20 conflict-affected municipalities, with 50% of loans going to women; (4) Improved capacity of at least 5,000 farmers to manage agricultural businesses, including 3,000 women.</narrative>
    </description>
   </indicator>
  </result>
